Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Question}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.65,0:00:04.28,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It’s time to begin, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.28,0:00:07.49,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’ll be giving today’s PokéProblem!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.99,0:00:12.99,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,How will today’s battle between \N Lucario and Agoyon end?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.50,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Get the answer at the end of the episode!
Comment: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.46,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The exhibition match between...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.46,0:00:23.84,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...the Alola Pokémon League’s first Champion Satoshi \N and Kukui, a.k.a. Royal Mask.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.47,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This 6v6 full battle...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.47,0:00:30.18,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...turned into an intense clash with \N frequent switch-outs.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.14,0:00:33.76,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Professor Kukui kept up \N a powerful offense,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.31,0:00:37.14,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,but Satoshi and his Pokémon \N fought back with intense resolve.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.60,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Both sides now have three Pokémon left.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.60,0:00:46.11,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The battle now enters a showdown between \N Satoshi’s Agoyon and Professor Kukui’s Lucario.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.45,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Here we go! Scissor Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.07,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Infight!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.21,0:01:01.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.67,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Lucario leaps up!
Comment: 10,0:01:15.47,0:01:15.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 10,0:02:43.52,0:02:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.62,0:03:05.04,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Agoyon’s Scissor Cross attack \N missed its mark!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.50,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Lucario’s Infight \N seems to have dealt damage!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.00,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Agoyon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.26,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s the spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.02,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,It’s responding loud and clear \N to Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun}’s voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.15,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun} has built a friendship with it \N ever since it was a Bebenom.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.15,0:03:30.69,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Agoyon is now battling \N for Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun}’s sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.57,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,This is friendship! \N Friendship indeed!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.57,0:03:40.28,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Friendship gives rise to \N heated battles!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.54,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Don’t let your guard down.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.54,0:03:48.25,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You managed to land the first hit, \N but this is still a foe we know little about.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go! Sludge Bomb!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.09,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Charge in!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.39,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, no! That’s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.72,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Dragon Pulse!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.10,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Poison-type moves have \N no effect on Steel types!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.73,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Sludge Bomb will not work \N on Lucario!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.07,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.96,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Infight!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Scissor Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.77,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Agoyon lands Scissor Cross this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Right! Good going, Agoyon! {Suggesting "All right!" in place of "Right!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.11,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,That was a quick reaction-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.44,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.48,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,It’s gotten into the rhythm of battling!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.20,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Seems they’re evenly matched.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.36,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.74,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Divine Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.21,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Use Scissor Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.46,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.51,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Divine Speed is fearsome!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.51,0:05:27.89,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Lucario is even faster \N than the soaring Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.44,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I couldn’t see it at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.98,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Lucario’s movements are \N impeccably precise!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.98,0:05:39.44,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Offense... Defense... Speed... \N They’re perfectly balanced-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.41,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon, please stand up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.75,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Agoyon is back!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.55,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You can still go on, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.43,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Glad to see it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.43,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,They can see through \N our movements...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.68,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.64,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I’m sure you’ll use...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.68,Main,Kukui & Satoshi,0,0,0,,Dragon Pulse!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.20,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,It’s a Dragon Pulse clash!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.99,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Such power!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.58,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go, Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.59,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Here they come, Lucario! \N Infight!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.59,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Scissor Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.97,0:06:51.93,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Lucario stopped Agoyon again! \N It’s read its opponent perfectly!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.48,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Dragon Pulse!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.24,0:07:06.53,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Dragon Pulse makes impact!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.34,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Lucario is unable to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.34,0:07:31.22,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Lucario is eliminated! \N Agoyon wins its battle debut!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.43,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! You did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.40,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You look just like Bebenom \N when you do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.24,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,They won! Incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.24,0:07:52.33,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Agoyon’s battle data \N has been updated-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.54,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,A huge victory for Goyo-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.96,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Return, Lucario.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.17,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Didn’t expect that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.09,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You copied what I did \N to beat Melmetal, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.30,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Well, if I just battled normally,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.27,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,there’s no way I could’ve \N landed a hit on your Lucario!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.77,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,A sharp wit to adapt \N to the situation at hand... {Line reads a little odd to me but I can't think of anything to suggest, leave it if it seems fine to you. It's possible I've just never seen this expression. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.90,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,And your Pokémon answering in turn...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.27,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You guys really are incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.82,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon, take a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.75,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Oh? He won’t keep going with Agoyon?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.21,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You did great in your first battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.71,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,A Fire Pledge, huh, Satoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.47,Main,Kukui & Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.90,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Gaogaen and Nyaheat \N face off once more!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.28,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The time has finally come!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.36,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,How will Nyaheat fight, \N now that he’s powered up?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.95,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I can feel the tension in the air!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.95,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Isn’t this exciting, Garagara?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.29,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.79,0:09:27.59,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Ever since their first clash, it’s like there’s been \N invisible sparks flying between these two!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.26,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Let the battle begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.72,0:09:34.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat, don’t be hasty.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Watch Gaogaen’s movements carefully!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.55,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.55,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,{\an8}DD Lariat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.27,0:10:24.52,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,They have made their move! \N Will the winner be Gaogaen or Nyaheat?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.82,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon!
Comment: 10,0:10:30.53,0:10:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.49,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.84,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Nyaheat is so quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.21,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Fire Fang!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.34,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hell Thrust!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.10,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It really is tough!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.10,0:11:11.11,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Were they using this first round \N to size each other up, perhaps?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.11,0:11:15.61,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi! \N I could really feel Nyaheat’s power!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.12,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This is just the beginning! \N We’re gonna keep impressing you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.99,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.75,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Gaogaen! Build Up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.34,0:11:33.26,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Use Great Blaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.26,0:11:33.26,Main,Starfish keeping count of how often an overused track is overused,0,0,0,,{Heated Fire Showdown play count in the Alola League: 9 -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.35,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You were {\i1}that{\i0} strong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.99,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Gaogaen wins the showdown between \N Great Blaze and Build Up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.66,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,But the flames are intense!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.08,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nitro Charge!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.56,0:12:27.18,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,So fast! Nyaheat blurs into \N nothing but a red flash!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.94,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Nyabi-chan seems \N rather obsessed with Gao-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.48,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Ever since they first met,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.90,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Gaogaen’s been like a massive wall \N for Nyaheat to overcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.95,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,He’s challenged it several times, \N but never won.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.95,0:12:44.16,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Satoshi tends to partner up with \N a lot of highly competitive Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.70,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,They flock to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.16,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Fire Fang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.17,0:12:57.84,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Oh, my! \N Gaogaen grabbed Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.84,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,It’s got a firm grip \N and won’t let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.18,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,He won’t get out of \N that grasp easily!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.85,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Him raising his speed \N won’t help here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.98,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Let’s see you fight back \N from {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.11,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Things seem hopeless for Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.79,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hell Thrust!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.38,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.07,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s right, Nyaheat! \N We can still go on!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.70,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Blaze up, Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Go, Nyaheat! Use Revenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.89,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Revenge hits its mark!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.39,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Gaogaen’s down on one knee!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,How’s that, Gaogaen?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.73,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,That was intense!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.86,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I didn’t know Revenge \N was that strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.40,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Its power is greater than ever-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.57,0:14:46.45,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Can Gaogaen recover from this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.17,0:15:02.67,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Gaogaen and Nyaheat’s flames \N flare up to full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.88,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This build-up of flames...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.18,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Now’s the time to end this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.19,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.28,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.78,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.58,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,A face-off between two Z-Moves?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.58,0:15:34.00,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This is our full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.59,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Burn with passion, Gaogaen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.59,0:15:43.55,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Set the field ablaze \N with the ultimate flames!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.34,0:15:51.10,Main,Kukui & Satoshi,0,0,0,,Dynamic Full Flame!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.91,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Both fighters use Dynamic Full Flame!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.91,0:16:19.08,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Their Z-Moves clash and turn into a massive fireball \N that consumes the battlefield!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.02,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat! Let’s finish this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.86,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Gaogaen! \N Use Hell Thrust!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.29,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Gaogaen is unable to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.29,0:17:47.25,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Down! Gaogaen is down!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.67,0:17:51.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right, Nyaheat, you did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.04,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,He evolved!{NOOOOOO series ruined. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.75,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,I can’t believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.75,0:18:26.17,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Amazing! Following its victory, \N Nyaheat evolved!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.55,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Amazing, Gaogaen! \N Keep it up for the last one!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.18,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Gaogaen... You’re...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.90,0:18:50.65,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Gaogaen is unable to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.53,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,The battle reached \N a shocking conclusion!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.24,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,After grasping victory {\i1}and{\i0} evolving,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.91,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi’s Gaogaen \N goes down, as well!{Can I just point out that the way this whole thing is presented, Satoshi-Gaogaen... kinda looks straight-up DEAD? I mean one would assume he would have collapsed in that case, but then I would also assume that from him losing consciousness. So... yeah. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.12,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.41,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Is this even possible?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.67,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Gaogaen, you were really cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.67,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I won’t let your effort go to waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.72,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Listen to this applause!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.72,0:19:25.21,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi and Nyaheat— \N No, the evolved Gaogaen...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.81,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,check,...are being showered with applause \N for their performance!{Should be shorter}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.23,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Return, Gaogaen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.73,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,That was a great fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.40,0:19:35.57,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi! This still isn’t over!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.16,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Of course not! \N We’ll clash at full power ‘til the very end!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.08,0:19:44.83,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Let us resume the battle! \N Both sides, send out your Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.54,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.76,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,It’s Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.26,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,What is it doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.55,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Surely it cannot be enraged?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.85,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.72,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko has appeared \N on Manalo Stadium!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.19,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what’s...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.24,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You mean you want to battle us?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.58,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Are you serious, \N Kapu-Kokeko?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.20,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,It seems young Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun} \N is exactly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.87,0:20:31.21,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko wishes to battle by your side \N against young Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun} and his Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.22,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko! \N We don’t mind! Let’s do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.97,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,This just got really interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.05,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.68,0:20:47.02,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,How about all of you? \N Do you want to see Kapu-Kokeko battle?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.81,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That’s just incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.73,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Yeah! I gotta see this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.86,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I’ve never even {\i1}read{\i0} \N about a battle like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.99,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,This exhibition match is the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.65,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,We’ll cheer them on at full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.16,0:21:06.20,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,A team-up between Kukui{honorific note: Kukui-kun} \N and Kapu-Kokeko! This’ll be intense!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.20,0:21:11.17,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Who would have thought an Alolan Guardian Deity \N would battle under the command of a trainer?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.50,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,This is spectacular!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.63,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Counting on you, Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.47,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.64,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let me fight with this guy first!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.73,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi rises \N to the challenge with Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.10,0:21:35.52,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,An Ultra Beast VS an Alolan legend! \N This will be a {\i1}marvelous{\i0} showdown!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.98,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,I feel romanticism in the air!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.49,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,It’s giving me chills!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.62,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Electric Field, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.62,0:21:47.08,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko! Let’s battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.62,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The exhibition match \N has taken an unexpected turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.62,0:21:54.13,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,How will Satoshi face Kapu-Kokeko?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.17,Main,Narrator,300,0,0,,Next time: \N The conclusion!
Comment: 10,0:21:59.51,0:21:59.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 10,0:23:20.50,0:23:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.55,0:23:25.30,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.30,0:23:30.26,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The battle between Lucario and Agoyon \N ended in victory for Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.26,0:23:33.98,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The Guiding Waves Pokémon Lucario \N is a Fighting/Steel type.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.98,0:23:40.57,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,They say it can sense the feelings of people and Pokémon \N from a kilometer away! Incredible!{This statement is repeated in several game dex entries but I didn’t think any of their phrasings were QUITE exact enough to match the JP here, so... My own translation. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.57,0:23:43.69,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,But Agoyon sure was strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.49,0:23:49.95,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Let’s see... \N Kapu-Kokeko’s moves are...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.95,0:23:55.29,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Wonderful! This sort of surprise \N lights a fire in my announcer soul!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.21,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Comment: 10,0:24:00.54,0:24:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.50,0:24:04.42,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You really have made it far, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.42,0:24:06.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.17,0:24:11.85,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,The bond between teacher and student... \N Between Alolan parent and child... It brings a tear to my eye!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.10,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Here’s your coat!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.10,0:24:15.73,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Yeah, it’s all clean!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.73,0:24:17.10,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Here’s your shoes!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.10,0:24:19.52,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Yeah! They’re shining!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.52,0:24:21.19,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Well done, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.19,0:24:23.40,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,What are you even {\i1}talking{\i0} about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.40,0:24:25.53,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.53,0:24:30.49,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Alola’s Mightiest Z! Kapu-Kokeko VS Pikachu!!
