Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.56,0:01:19.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:19.98,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.98,0:01:26.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:26.27,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}{\fad(0,300)}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.62,OP,,0,0,0,,You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.62,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.62,0:01:43.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:43.37,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}{\be3\bord9}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.37,0:01:47.88,OP,,0,0,0,,Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:47.88,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.88,0:01:53.13,OP,,0,0,0,,will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:53.13,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.47,OP,,0,0,0,,Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.47,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.56,OP,,0,0,0,,playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.56,OP,,0,0,0,,go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.77,OP,,0,0,0,,You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.77,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.77,0:02:11.65,OP,,0,0,0,,how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:11.65,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.07,OP,,0,0,0,,Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.07,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.07,0:02:21.95,OP,,0,0,0,,Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:21.95,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.83,OP,,0,0,0,,Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.83,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.92,OP,,0,0,0,,With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.92,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.93,OP,,0,0,0,,It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.93,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.93,0:02:43.52,OP,,0,0,0,,Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:43.52,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:43.52,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=5}
