Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}How long has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.31,EDp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}How long has it been
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.31,0:22:18.36,ED,,0,0,0,,since I bid Masara Town farewell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:18.36,EDp2,,0,0,0,,since I bid Masara Town farewell?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.45,ED,,0,0,0,,Got so many cuts, scratches, and friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.45,EDp2,,0,0,0,,Got so many cuts, scratches, and friends
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.45,0:22:24.57,ED,,0,0,0,,I’m kinda proud of that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:24.57,EDp2,,0,0,0,,I’m kinda proud of that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.28,ED,,0,0,0,,The sneakers I rushed out to buy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.28,EDp2,,0,0,0,,The sneakers I rushed out to buy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.28,0:22:30.37,ED,,0,0,0,,back when they were the latest trend...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:30.37,EDp2,,0,0,0,,back when they were the latest trend...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.54,ED,,0,0,0,,...are now one of a kind, no others like them in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.54,EDp2,,0,0,0,,...are now one of a kind, no others like them in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.54,0:22:44.05,ED,,0,0,0,,They’re the best worn-out shoes around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:44.05,EDp2,,0,0,0,,They’re the best worn-out shoes around!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.14,ED,,0,0,0,,Before I know it... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.14,EDp2,,0,0,0,,Before I know it... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.14,0:22:51.35,ED,,0,0,0,,Little by little... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:51.35,EDp2,,0,0,0,,Little by little... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.14,ED,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna become... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.14,EDp2,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna become... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.14,0:23:01.15,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...way stronger than I am! Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:23:01.15,EDp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...way stronger than I am! Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.61,0:23:12.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}And someday I’ll have the chance to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:12.29,EDp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}And someday I’ll have the chance to say...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.29,0:23:17.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}“Hello, my dream”
